{"tid":442364,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋公仔］巴打絲打求救 揾唔番買呢隻野果間鋪","createTime":"2017-10-20T14:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T05:06:50.000Z","uid":33391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a05303f92df30549df888489b2debd94841ea1","tid":442364,"uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/222127_1e28b08dde8f0f4f9ea73e16f51466b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F222127_1e28b08dde8f0f4f9ea73e16f51466b7.jpg&h=51362537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻熊仔係我大約03年果陣喺奧海城嘅一間鋪頭買 果陣超鐘意佢 日日攬住佢瞓 點知有一次帶佢去旅行走果陣就唔見左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大海撈針 如果有巴絲打知道邊到可以揾番佢嘅就話比我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知張相好矇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻熊仔身係白色，着住一件連帽嘅灰白間條hoodies㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求大神相助"},{"pid":"1faeddc69cd574124f2425a7c7e6a05e98a01f1a","tid":442364,"uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53f86ec881d3e5f4297a278d038906c4cd8984bc","tid":442364,"uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8eebf2d64834c4a2b47f57bc8d3c48db81b883e","tid":442364,"uid":154871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a164105924dfeaa325886dea3126cfc854c3d","tid":442364,"uid":154736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c6aa4a0ca664fac383b7d6154a50411d116615